Cyberpunk style: A neon-drenched server room at night where streams of glowing cyan and magenta data packets flow between floating holographic tokens - crystalline hexagonal badges with intricate circuit patterns etched into their surfaces. One token splits into two, its digital essence transferring through luminous fiber optic cables that snake through the dark metallic environment. The scene shows a seamless handoff of identity, with the original token dissolving into particles while a new, freshly-minted token materializes nearby, pulsing with electric energy. Rain streaks across industrial glass panels in the background, reflecting the ambient glow. Chrome surfaces and exposed conduits frame the composition, with subtle purple fog rolling along the floor.
